==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inopportune
<hw>In*op`por*tune"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inopportunus</ets>: cf. F. <ets>inopportun</ets>. See <er>In-</er>
not, and <er>Opportune</er>.]</ety> <def>Not opportune; inconvenient;
unseasonable; <as>as, an <ex>inopportune</ex> occurrence, remark,
etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No visit could have been more <qex>inopportune</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>T. Hook.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inopportunely</ent>⟦br⟧
